trans-unit.source: The `CONNECTDATA` structure is the type enumerated through the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.UCOMIEnumConnections.Next%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: `CONNECTDATA`结构是通过枚举的类型<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.UCOMIEnumConnections.Next%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法。</xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.UCOMIEnumConnections.Next%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息`CONNECTDATA`，请参阅 MSDN 库。

trans-unit.source: Represents a connection token that is returned from a call to <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.UCOMIConnectionPoint.Advise%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个连接令牌，从调用返回<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.UCOMIConnectionPoint.Advise%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: Represents a pointer to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IUnknown" name="IUnknown" href=""></xref> interface on a connected advisory sink.
trans-unit.target: 表示指向的指针<xref uid="langword_csharp_IUnknown" name="IUnknown" href=""></xref>连接的通知接收器上的接口。

trans-unit.source: The caller must call <xref uid="langword_csharp_IUnknown::Release" name="IUnknown::Release" href=""></xref> on this pointer when the <xref uid="langword_csharp_CONNECTDATA" name="CONNECTDATA" href=""></xref> structure is no longer needed.
trans-unit.target: 调用方必须调用<xref uid="langword_csharp_IUnknown::Release" name="IUnknown::Release" href=""> </xref> this 指针上时<xref uid="langword_csharp_CONNECTDATA" name="CONNECTDATA" href=""></xref>不再需要结构。
